{"tid":435962,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4]FIFA18 PRO CLUB 招新球員(3-4-2-1)","createTime":"2017-10-14T17:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T08:21:33.000Z","uid":10175,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64ac4b321ff7b1ce7b4f27b3b9d0f401bc5324c2","tid":435962,"uid":10175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T17:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">新創球會</span>, 希望以參加 <span style=\"color: gold;\">VPL</span> 比賽 增加球會經驗為目標.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球會陣式：343 (3-4-2-1)，以三中堅為球隊基本陣型，小組短傳為主，不會胡亂吊高波及長傳。這個陣式最重要是翼衛，<br />\n記住八個字：進攻拉闊，防守收窄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本球會現正招收以下位置<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">CB/LCB/RCB</span> 三中堅 (各一名)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">LWB/RWB</span> 右翼衛 (一名)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">RCM</span>  右中場 (一名)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">RF</span> 右翼 (一名)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">GK</span> 龍門 (一名)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n球會常上線球員有4人, 希望招收一些<span style=\"color: gold;\">常上線</span>, <span style=\"color: gold;\">不會經常轉隊踢</span>或有幾隊係身,<span style=\"color: gold;\">會用咪</span>,性格開朗之隊友.<br />\n球會一星期最少五天以上會上線, 時間為晚上9:30~3:00(大約),星期六日及假期會看球隊上線人數再決定.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如有興趣者可 TG:   <a href=\"https://t.me/Cart_Noodle\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCart_Noodle&d=3kdSw36gXA8gdioUiDeTTDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=8e9f3188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Cart_Noodle</a><br />\n<br />\n可寫下要求位置及留下psn方便本人加你試腳.<br />\n<br />\n謝謝."},{"pid":"8db49c2b9e01d42c46111695ec17bc6afa14ac23","tid":435962,"uid":10175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T07:53:41.000Z","msg":"推~~~~"},{"pid":"939279c39f4f9a811cf9de6d3f094cbb905a98d5","tid":435962,"uid":15511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T12:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a03d5d997454c16649db8bfb